// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mltyzM asymmetric blocks gcd subdivided, 2023 by jt
// subdivides https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdcBR2 asymmetric blocks compactified
// by applying https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mltyRM binary gcd

// Subdivide the integer rectangles of the asymmetric/irregular blocks pattern
// (random-blocks-by-alternating-double-T-crossings) into squares
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdcBR2 asymmetric blocks compactified
// by applying the https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mltyRM binary gcd algorithm.

// For a more complex application see for example
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtccWn industrial storage facility

// tags: t, blocks, double, alternating, irregular, asymmetric,binary, algorithm, euclidean, subdivision, gcd, common, greatest, divisor

